Commentary: That such an observation should have passed as evident at the
  time the Quran was revealed shows to what extent the vision of modern man
  has atrophied.
---
Have not the disbelievers seen that the heavens and the earth were of one
piece? Then We parted them asunder, and from the water We made every living
thing.
